	* ircd/s_auth.c (auth_set_username): Check if the last
	character of the username is alphanumeric, instead of the
	'\0' terminator.
	
	* ircd/m_pong.c (mr_pong): Parse cookie with strtoul(),
	since atol() causes signedness problems.

