	* ircd/m_topic.c: Remove block comment about sptr, cptr, etc.
	(do_settopic): Add doxygen comment. Move permissions checks..
	(m_topic): .. to here.  Update doxygen comment.
	(ms_topic): Update doxygen comment here too.

