	'o' in RPL_STATSOLINE.

	* ircd/s_stats.c (stats_configured_links): In /stats o/O, display
	'O' if either the oper block or the connection class has
	PRIV_PROPAGATE (global oper) and 'o' if neither has PRIV_PROPAGATE
	(local oper).

