2005-04-09  Kevin L. Mitchell  <klmitch@mit.edu>

	* ircd/ircd.c: conditionally include sys/resource.h; otherwise,
	RLIMIT_CORE will not be defined and so set_core_limit() will never
	be defined, much less run.

